chorechill-ctl (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Transition to modular plugin-based driver architecture
  * Add DMI-based hardware auto-detection utility (chorechill-detect)
  * Add native Debian packaging (.deb) support
  * Add MSI Modern EC driver plugin (plugin_msi_modern.so)
  * Deprecate monolithic install.sh in favor of dpkg/apt installation

